{
  "texts": [
    "The analysis pipeline we present for turnover analysis represents a novel contribution.",
    "In this section, some specific information on the data analysis pipeline described in the methodology is presented, including the prediction results provided by the ensemble model.",
    "The method is suitable to solve almost any classification problem.",
    "In this research, we apply the method to the prediction of node labels.",
    "The label in our case can take two values: 1 if the worker leaves, 0 if he stays."
  ]
}